{%- comment -%}
  SBJ / SKIMS-match MEGA-MENU CSS — global (all pages, header lives on every page).

  WHY A SNIPPET (read before moving it):
  Loaded once from layout/theme.liquid near </body> so it wins source-order over
  base.css :root tokens and the header block's own <style>, and so theme-editor
  saves never revert it (same pattern as sbj-footer-css / sbj-home-css).

  WHAT IT DOES (matches the SKIMS mega menu the user filmed):
   1. Makes the dropdown open/close FAST + smooth (base.css ships 360ms — too slow).
   2. Adds the "small brown animation": an animated sienna (#986B58) underline that
      slides in under the hovered / open top-level nav link (SKIMS nav-hover accent).
   3. Tightens the panel so it's "properly sized" (less cavernous vertical padding).
  Covers ONLY what native settings cannot. No HTML changes.
{%- endcomment -%}
<style>
/* ---- 1. Snappy open/close (SKIMS feel) ----------------------------------- */
/* base.css sets --submenu-animation-speed:360ms in :root; this later :root wins. */
:root {
  --submenu-animation-speed: 140ms;
}
/* A crisper ease-out so the reveal "snaps" open instead of drifting. */
#header-component .menu-list__list-item:not([slot='overflow']) > .menu-list__submenu,
#header-component .overflow-menu::part(overflow),
#header-component .header__underlay-open {
  transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.22, 0.61, 0.36, 1) !important;
}

/* ---- 1b. INSTANT hover switching (the real speed fix) -------------------- *
 * Horizon paints an invisible "safety box" (.menu-list__link[data-safety-box]
 * ::after) that overlays the area under the active link WHILE the pointer is
 * moving, so sweeping across the nav does nothing until you STOP — the freeze.
 * Killing it lets each item fire pointerenter the instant the cursor crosses
 * it, so the panel follows the cursor live in both directions (like SKIMS).
 * The small link->submenu bridge (.menu-list__list-item::after) is untouched,
 * so moving down into the open panel still keeps it open. */
#header-component .menu-list__link[data-safety-box='true']::after {
  display: none !important;
}

/* ---- 2. Brown sienna underline under top-level links ---------------------- */
#header-component {
  --sbj-nav-accent: #986B58; /* SKIMS "sienna / secondary" nav-hover underline */
}
/* The text span inside each top-level link. We anchor an underline bar to it. */
#header-component .menu-list__list-item:not([slot='overflow']) .menu-list__link-title {
  position: relative;
}
#header-component .menu-list__list-item:not([slot='overflow']) .menu-list__link-title::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  left: calc(var(--gap-xl) / 2);
  right: calc(var(--gap-xl) / 2);
  bottom: -5px;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--sbj-nav-accent);
  transform: scaleX(0);
  transform-origin: left center;
  transition: transform 180ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 0.61, 0.36, 1);
  pointer-events: none;
}
/* Slide it in on hover, keyboard focus, and while the mega panel is open. */
#header-component .menu-list__list-item:not([slot='overflow']):hover .menu-list__link-title::after,
#header-component .menu-list__list-item:not([slot='overflow']):focus-within .menu-list__link-title::after,
#header-component .menu-list__list-item:not([slot='overflow']) .menu-list__link[aria-expanded='true'] .menu-list__link-title::after {
  transform: scaleX(1);
}

/* ---- 3. Properly-sized panel + faster content fade ----------------------- */
/* base.css uses --padding-3xl top & bottom — cavernous. Trim to SKIMS proportions. */
#header-component .menu-list__submenu,
#header-component .overflow-menu::part(overflow) {
  --submenu-padding-block-start: var(--padding-lg);
  --submenu-padding-block-end: var(--padding-xl);
}
/* Content fades a touch quicker than the clip reveal so it never lags behind. */
#header-component .menu-list__list-item:not([slot='overflow']) > .menu-list__submenu,
#header-component .overflow-menu::part(overflow) {
  --submenu-content-animation: opacity calc(var(--submenu-animation-speed) * 0.6) ease-out;
}

/* ---- 4. Mega-menu content typography + featured tiles (SKIMS pic 4 look) -------
 * SKIMS panel: bold Title-Case column headings, regular Inter sub-links with roomy
 * line-height, and featured tiles that are image + title (NO price). This styles the
 * existing content to SKIMS proportions; the multi-column sub-heading structure fills
 * in once the navigation has nested groups. */

/* Column heading / standalone bold links (the L2 nav items) */
#header-component .mega-menu__link--parent,
#header-component .mega-menu__column > div > .mega-menu__link {
  font-family: "Inter", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;
  font-size: 14px !important;
  font-weight: 700 !important;
  line-height: 20px !important;
  letter-spacing: normal !important;
  text-transform: none !important;
  color: #2D2A26 !important;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

/* Sub-links under a heading (the L3 nav items) — regular Inter, roomy */
#header-component .mega-menu__column ul .mega-menu__link {
  font-family: "Inter", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;
  font-size: 14px !important;
  font-weight: 400 !important;
  line-height: 30px !important;
  letter-spacing: normal !important;
  text-transform: none !important;
  color: #2D2A26 !important;
  padding: 0 !important;
}
#header-component .mega-menu__column ul .mega-menu__link:hover {
  color: #986B58 !important; /* SKIMS sienna hover */
}

/* Featured tiles: SKIMS shows image + title only (no price). */
#header-component .mega-menu__content .price,
#header-component .mega-menu__content [class*="price"] {
  display: none !important;
}
#header-component .mega-menu__content .product-card__content .user-select-text,
#header-component .mega-menu__content .product-card__content .user-select-text :is(p, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6) {
  font-family: "Inter", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif !important;
  font-size: 14px !important;
  font-weight: 700 !important;
  line-height: 18px !important;
  letter-spacing: normal !important;
  text-transform: none !important;
  color: #2D2A26 !important;
}
/* Show two featured tiles like SKIMS (hide the 3rd) and give them room. */
#header-component .mega-menu__content-list--products { gap: 18px !important; }
#header-component .mega-menu__content-list--products .mega-menu__content-list-item:nth-child(n+3) {
  display: none !important;
}
</style>
